So, you know.

00:51:16.300 --> 00:51:18.380
Yeah, that's exactly the same in Oregon here.

00:51:18.620 --> 00:51:20.300
So it's a good time to get stuff done.

00:51:21.400 --> 00:51:21.700
Yeah, exactly.

00:51:22.000 --> 00:51:22.220
So, yeah.

00:51:22.900 --> 00:51:28.620
And then I've been speaking to people from Shiny and Plotly about potentially looking into novels.

00:51:30.520 --> 00:51:31.180
Oh, that's cool.

