and learned some new things.

00:51:50.290 --> 00:51:52.340
If it does work, then great, exciting.

00:51:54.560 --> 00:51:56.180
So that's my top priority,

00:51:56.310 --> 00:52:01.220
and it's been really pleasing to see the community develop around NowWells.

00:52:01.320 --> 00:52:03.860
I really thought it would be a one-person project for a long time,

00:52:04.080 --> 00:52:07.400
but so many people have been contributing really high-quality pull requests.

00:52:08.360 --> 00:52:13.220
it's really been, yes, you've got to do, okay, one of them is this, okay, maybe a couple of them

00:52:13.360 --> 00:52:20.740
here are like GitHub bots, this pre-commit CI bot. Yeah, maybe 40, 30, but still, that's a lot.

00:52:21.800 --> 00:52:24.220
And while we're talking numbers on the homepage, I also want to point out

00:52:25.280 --> 00:52:28.580
10 million downloads a month is, there's a lot of downloads. That's awesome.

00:52:28.760 --> 00:52:34.240
Yeah, that's maybe slightly misleading because they pretty much just come from the fact that it's

00:52:34.200 --> 00:52:36.500
It's now a required dependency of Altair.

